snippet.title: Hypnosis of Corruption - Official Trailer
snippet.description:
You play as Hinata Yuzuzaka, a student of Hypnosis University. When strange things start happening around the town, Hinata starts to investigate. Can she uncover the cause of the mysterious happenings sweeping through town?
